  "keyFeatures": [
    "WhatsApp gateway (receive, store, route messages via whatsmeow)",
    "MCP server for external AI agents (Claude, OpenCode) to read and reply",
    "Anti-ban governor: rate limits, human-pacing delays, kill switch, reconnect backoff",
    "Per-chat routing: whitelist, auto mode (cheap API) vs advanced mode (MCP agent)",
    "Pwnagotchi-style e-paper kaomoji face with eye gaze animations and mood states",
    "Self-calibrating CW2015 battery gauge with linearized level and adaptive time-remaining",
    "Built-in web dashboard: battery chart, WhatsApp link/QR, rules, rate limits",
    "Bearer-token MCP auth (fail-closed endpoint)",
    "Session backup/restore with scrypt-encrypted snapshots",
    "MCP anti-flood guard to block runaway AI agents",
    "status.json data contract between core and display adapter",
    "Fully configurable via environment variables — zero hardcode"
  ],
